Hi Alex, I have a question about my recent bill. My name is Jamie.

Sure, my customer ID is one two three four five.

Thank you, Alex. I appreciate your help.

You're welcome, Jamie. Thank you for your patience and for choosing West Barnstable Horse Hides. Have a great day!
